                                                                                                                                    storing, or transming informaon are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              PS-03(04)             individuals accessing a system processing, storing, or transming
                                                                                                                                    <PS-03(04)_ODP[01] informaon types> meet <PS-03(04)_ODP[02] cizenship
                                                                                                                                    requirements>.
